== Overview ==
We are having [https://guestlist.co/events/747255 Beginners Day] on Saturday May 27th 2023 from noon - 5pm. The goal is to show the basics of as many tools as possible. In 2016 we had a similar event and it was a great success.

== Volunteer ==
If you would like to volunteer reach out in Slack to Robot Ambassador, reply in the google discussion group thread, or email instructors AT heatsynclabs.org

== Schedule ==

Unless noted the schedule is noon - 5pm.

Sewing - Linda

Electronics - Ben and David

Soldering - Stephen and David G

BioChem Lab - Microscope demo with Greg

3d Printing - Jot and Bill

Laser Cutter - David C Noon - 3pm Paul 2pm - 5pm

Jewelry - Sarah

Vinyl Cutter - Joy noon - 2pm

Lock Picking - Joe

Tours of the Hackerspace - Nathan

More - TBD
